  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, Set<String>

    public class VariableNames
extends HashSet<String>
    Encapsulates a set of variable names used for building a generated historic query. Variable names (the keys in this collection) are specified using their plain name e.g., "var1" instead of the SPARQL syntax "?var1" or "$var1".
